The BDN uses FISC to automate the processing of our Accounts Receivable invoices. To best automate that, we added a standardized remittance slip and a machine-readable scanline to all of our outgoing invoices. These files document that process pretty much from start to finish, including a script to generate the scanline in NetSuite and a custom HTML/PDF template for printing the invoices.

You can download the required OCR-A Extended font at http://cooltext.com/Download-Font-OCR+A+Extended
